{"tid":2360273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"家屬委託律師盧思位俾人跟蹤","createTime":"2021-01-09T14:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T15:05:06.000Z","uid":372892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86d5df9807e9a815746c8713d347e04dc952a083","tid":2360273,"uid":372892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"深圳12港人案其中一名家屬委託律師盧思位懷疑被警察跟蹤，他形容是赤裸裸的人身威脅，認為事件對他的人身自由構成嚴重威脅。<br />\n<br />\n盧思位表示，他離開居住小區時，發現被幾個戴口罩的人跟蹤，質疑對方的身份，以及為何拍照跟蹤他，但對方拒絕回答，其中一人語氣疑似警察，又打電話要求派更多人到現場，阻止盧思位離開，盧思位說，他因事離開現場，其後到派出所報案。<br />\n<br />\n四川省司法廳計劃吊銷盧思位的律師執業證書，聽證會將於下星期三舉行。盧思位早前表示，相信處罰與「深圳12港人案」有關。 <br />\n<br />\nsource (RTHK)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n律師唔係 condemn"},{"pid":"3d1208a38935e7f1ba74abc657515f902469746a","tid":2360273,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8742d8529657fa035e5caf5d623a55e2705d0859","tid":2360273,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccafad8a070d4438dccc6eb28c8dd3052c23d402","tid":2360273,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:04:28.000Z","msg":"可以點幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492e40961593aa463c1ec15741c4763c2ad9fecc","tid":2360273,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"其實中國做律師真係搵命博"}]}